  "prompt": "Does Toptal ever do any discounts?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, Toptal, a global network of top freelance talent in fields such as software development, design, and finance, typically does not offer discounts or promotions. Toptal positions itself as a premium service, connecting clients with highly vetted professionals, and maintains a focus on quality rather than price reductions.\n\nHowever, it\u2019s always a good idea to:\n- Check Toptal\u2019s official website or contact their sales team for the most up-to-date information.\n- Look for occasional referral programs or partnerships that might include benefits for new clients.\n- Negotiate terms directly if you\u2019re hiring for a large or long-term project.\n\nIf you\u2019re considering Toptal for your business needs, focus on the value and expertise they provide rather than expecting discounts.",
